{{emote|*Zanya taps their chin pensively.*}} 

Not much to tell about this place, we all keep pretty much t'ourselves. Some o' the others tend to the pig farms, and prepare the cheese. Right o'er there is the 'orkshop of Imimiw, our tinker. She'll set any 'ires straight in just a moment. 

There is the occasional traveler, but otherwise the days are spent working, trading and napping un'er the Hind Sun.

